01_Fall_Exams.description: All exam materials (midterms, finals, solutions, tagged, walkthroughs) for Fall semesters, grouped by year and exam type.

02_Spring_Exams.description: All exam materials (midterms, finals, solutions, tagged, walkthroughs) for Spring semesters, grouped by year and exam type.

03_Summer_Exams.description: All exam materials (midterms, finals, diagnostics, solutions, practice exams, walkthroughs) for Summer semesters, grouped by year and exam type.

04_Study_Guides_and_Practice.description: Study guides, practice exams, and their solutions, regardless of semester. Includes any materials from 'study-guide/' or with 'practice' in the folder or filename.

05_Exam_Walkthrough_Videos.description: All YouTube or video walkthroughs for any exam, regardless of semester. Includes .mp4, .mkv, .webm files and any .html links to walkthroughs.

06_Other_Exam_Files.description: Miscellaneous exam-related files not clearly falling into the above categories (e.g., zip archives, special formats, or uncategorized files).

structure_design.reasoning: A chronological structure by semester (Fall, Spring, Summer) best reflects how students and instructors reference exams. Each folder groups all exam types (midterms, finals, solutions, walkthroughs) for that term, regardless of file type. Study guides and practice materials are grouped separately due to their cross-semester relevance. Walkthrough videos are also grouped for easy access. This structure balances semantic grouping (by exam session) with practical retrieval, and is liberal in grouping related content even if file naming varies.
